A session titled "The Distance between Metaverse and Us" drew great attention at the 2022 Boao Forum for Asia, which was held from April 20 to 22 in south China's Hainan Province. Guests of the session were mainly leaders from tech companies, such as Huawei, Nvidia and iFLYTEK. They touched on topics such as opportunities, risks and future governance of the metaverse, and how the development technology can create more application scenarios of the metaverse. CGTN's Guo Meiping attended the session. Let's hear about her thoughts on the new concept of the metaverse. Videographer: Qi Jianqiang Video editor: Qi Jianqiang Cover image: Yu Peng Producer: Wang Kailin Chief editor: Wu Gang Supervisor: Liu Yuqi